com.outbrain.aletheia.datum.consumption

Interface DatumConsumerStream<TDomainClass>

  • Type Parameters:
    TDomainClass - The type of the datum to be consumed by this DatumConsumerStream.
    All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AuditingDatumConsumerStream

    public interface DatumConsumerStream<TDomainClass>
extends AutoCloseable
    The base interface for a DatumConsumerStream, capable of providing clients with datum instances consumed from a data source.
